Operation","history":"/rest/api/content/2857533489/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2857533489/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2857533489/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2857533489","tinyui":"/x/MYBSqg","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2857533489","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2857533489/Tasking+y+Estimaci+n+-+Red+N1","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2857533489"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"info\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"f7303145-63c1-4122-9a28-54c83bd59f0f\"><ac:rich-text-body><p /></ac:rich-text-body></ac:structured-macro><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"c941905e-cc65-47cb-b22a-830f93c99168\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 472.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 108.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 177.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Estimaci&oacute;n (hs)</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Servicio / Portal</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar endpoint de index para los product_reversal_rules.</p><p><em>Usar picasso listing.</em></p><p><em>Reversal-service no usa Picasso Listing para nada, por ende esta tarea implica agregarlo, configurarlo y usarlo para esta tarea.</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">32</p></td><td><p>reversal-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar endpoint para obtener la <code>ReversalCutOffTimeRule</code> actual.</p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">12</p></td><td><p>reversal-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar bot&oacute;n para ver listado de facturadores que no aceptan anulaciones en secci&oacute;n &ldquo;Mis Operaciones&rdquo; de InfoNet Cobranzas.</p><p><em>Probar dise&ntilde;os de bot&oacute;n y texto para dar que aparente ser un bot&oacute;n y no una alerta.</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">4</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Agregar bot&oacute;n para ver listado de facturadores que no aceptan anulaciones en secci&oacute;n &ldquo;Anulaciones&rdquo; del Portal de Comercios.</p><p><em>Reutilizar bot&oacute;n de IC</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">2</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear vista para listar todos los facturadores que no aceptan anulaciones en InfoNet Cobranzas</p><p><em>Incluye agregar stubs de las dos nuevas operaciones en bancard-services-stubs. </em></p><p><em>Incluye integraci&oacute;n con reversal-service (no se usa todav&iacute;a en el portal de comercios) </em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">30</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear vista para listar todos los facturadores que no aceptan anulaciones en Portal de Comercios</p><p /><p><em>Reutilizar partial creado para la vista de InfoNet Cobranzas</em></p></td><td><p style=\"text-align: center;\">8</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr></tbody></table><ac:adf-extension><ac:adf-node type=\"panel\"><ac:adf-attribute key=\"panel-type\">note</ac:adf-attribute><ac:adf-content><p><strong>Preguntas</strong></p><p>Las respuestas a estas preguntas no afectan en el tasking y la estimaci&oacute;n, pero sirve para aclarar dudas que tenemos respecto al flujo de reversas.</p></ac:adf-content></ac:adf-node><ac:adf-fallback><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" style=\"background-color: rgb(234,230,255);border-color: rgb(153,141,217);border-width: 1.0px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: rgb(234,230,255);\">\n<p><strong>Preguntas</strong></p><p>Las respuestas a estas preguntas no afectan en el tasking y la estimaci&oacute;n, pero sirve para aclarar dudas que tenemos respecto al flujo de reversas.</p>\n</div></div></ac:adf-fallback></ac:adf-extension><table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"c69b8187-9312-406b-80d4-cec9a24b48df\"><colgroup><col style=\"width: 448.0px;\" /><col style=\"width: 311.0px;\" /></colgroup><tbody><tr><td><p>rule_type solo puede ser <code>PROHIBITED_REVERSAL_RULE_TYPE</code> o <code>WITH_CUTOFF_RULE_TYPE</code>. No hay un tipo de regla que indique algo as&iacute; como &ldquo;reversa libre&ldquo; Los productos que no tienen ning&uacute;n tipo de restricci&oacute;n no est&aacute;n en la tabla?</p></td><td><p /></td></tr><tr><td><p>En reversal service SIEMPRE se valida el horario de restricci&oacute;n. Sin importar de que producto sea el pago que se quiere reversar:</p><ac:image ac:align=\"center\" ac:layout=\"center\" ac:original-height=\"107\" ac:original-width=\"762\" ac:custom-width=\"true\" ac:alt=\"image-20240613-135459.png\" ac:width=\"740\"><ri:attachment ri:filename=\"image-20240613-135459.png\" ri:version-at-save=\"1\" /></ac:image><p>Eso est&aacute; bien?</p></td><td><p /></td></tr></tbody></table><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3147104262"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":5321},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3147104262/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3147104262/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3147104262/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3147104262/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3147104262","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3147104262/Espacio+de+Listado+de+Facturadores+que+no+anulan","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3147104262","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3147104262","tinyui":"/x/BgCVuw","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}